    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="BeautifulSoup"><a href="#BeautifulSoup" class="headerlink" title="BeautifulSoup"></a>BeautifulSoup</h1><p>BeautifulSoup将复杂的HTML文档转换成一个复杂的树形结构，每个节点都是python对象。</p><a id="more"></a><p>对所有对象可以归纳为4种：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter hljs"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-comment"># - Tag</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># - NavigableString</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># - BeautifulSoup</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># - Comment</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> bs4 <span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> BeautifulSoup<br><br>file = <span class="hljs-built_in">open</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;解析目标文件路径&quot;</span>,<span class="hljs-string">&quot;rb&quot;</span>)  <span class="hljs-comment">#模拟爬取到的文件以二进制读取到内存中</span><br>html = file.read()  <span class="hljs-comment">#读取到一个对象中</span><br>bs = BeautifulSoup(html,<span class="hljs-string">&quot;html.parser&quot;</span>)  <span class="hljs-comment">#使用“html.parser”解析器解析一个之前定义的html对象</span><br><br>print(bs.title)<br>print(bs.title.string)<span class="hljs-comment">#可以单独打印其中的字符串</span><br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h2 id="四种类型"><a href="#四种类型" class="headerlink" title="四种类型"></a>四种类型</h2><h3 id="1-Tag"><a href="#1-Tag" class="headerlink" title="1.Tag"></a>1.Tag</h3><blockquote><p>标签及其内容</p></blockquote><p>例：</p><table><thead><tr><th align="center">方法</th><th align="center">效果</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="center">title</td><td align="center">获取title标签里的内容</td></tr><tr><td align="center">a</td><td align="center">获取a标签里的内容</td></tr></tbody></table><ul><li>通过此方法拿到的都是获取到的<font color="#00ffff">第一个</font>内容</li><li>以上只是示范通过使用其他标签就能获取到想要获取的内容</li></ul><h3 id="2-NavigableString"><a href="#2-NavigableString" class="headerlink" title="2.NavigableString"></a>2.NavigableString</h3><blockquote><p>标签里的内容(字符串)</p></blockquote><table><thead><tr><th align="center">方法</th><th align="center">效果</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="center">.attrs</td><td align="center">过滤掉标签以字典的方式获取到标签里的内容</td></tr></tbody></table><p>例：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter hljs"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs python">print(bs.a.attrs)<br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>以<code>attrs</code>获取到的数据以键值对的方式存储方便查找</li></ul><h3 id="3-BeautifulSoup"><a href="#3-BeautifulSoup" class="headerlink" title="3.BeautifulSoup"></a>3.BeautifulSoup</h3><blockquote><p>表示整个文档</p></blockquote><h3 id="4-Comment"><a href="#4-Comment" class="headerlink" title="4.Comment"></a>4.Comment</h3><blockquote><p>特殊的NavigableString，输出的内容不包括注释符号</p></blockquote><hr><h2 id="文档的搜索"><a href="#文档的搜索" class="headerlink" title="文档的搜索"></a>文档的搜索</h2><h3 id="1-find-all"><a href="#1-find-all" class="headerlink" title="1.find_all()"></a>1.find_all()</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter hljs"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> bs4 <span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> BeautifulSoup<br>file = <span class="hljs-built_in">open</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;目标文件&quot;</span>,<span class="hljs-string">&quot;rb&quot;</span>)<br>html = file.read()<br>bs = BeautifulSoup(html,<span class="hljs-string">&quot;html.parser&quot;</span>)<br><br>t_list = bs.find_all(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;a&quot;</span>)<span class="hljs-comment">#查找与&quot;a&quot;完全匹配的内容</span><br>print(t_list)<br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure><table><thead><tr><th align="center">方法</th><th align="center">效果</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="center"><code>find_all()</code></td><td align="center">查找与字符串<font color="#00ffff">完全匹配</font>的内容</td></tr></tbody></table><h3 id="2-正则表达式搜索"><a href="#2-正则表达式搜索" class="headerlink" title="2.正则表达式搜索"></a>2.正则表达式搜索</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter hljs"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> bs4 <span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> BeautifulSoup<br><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> re<br><br>file = <span class="hljs-built_in">open</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;目标文件&quot;</span>,<span class="hljs-string">&quot;rb&quot;</span>)<br>html = file.read()<br>bs = BeautifulSoup(html,<span class="hljs-string">&quot;html.parser&quot;</span>)<br><br><span class="hljs-comment">#编译一个正则表达式对象，通过find_all()方法查找符合的对象</span><br>t_list = bs.find_all(re.<span class="hljs-built_in">compile</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;a&quot;</span>))<br>print(t_list)<br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>通过此方法查找会查找到所有标签内包含“a”的数据</li></ul><blockquote><p>粗劣展示正则之后详解</p></blockquote><h3 id="3-方法-函数-方式搜索"><a href="#3-方法-函数-方式搜索" class="headerlink" title="3.方法(函数)方式搜索"></a>3.方法(函数)方式搜索</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter hljs"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span> <span class="hljs-title">name_is_exists</span>(<span class="hljs-params">tag</span>):</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> tag.has_attr(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;name&quot;</span>)<br><br>t_list = bs.find_all(name_is_exists)<br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>该方式仅做了解</li></ul><h3 id="4-kwargs-参数"><a href="#4-kwargs-参数" class="headerlink" title="4.kwargs 参数"></a>4.kwargs 参数</h3><p>例：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter hljs"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs python">t_list = bs.find_all(<span class="hljs-built_in">id</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;head&quot;</span>)<span class="hljs-comment">#查找关键词</span><br>t_list = bs.find_all(href=<span class="hljs-literal">True</span>)<span class="hljs-comment">#查找有链接的内容</span><br>t_list = bs.find_all(href=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;http://tieba.baidu.com&quot;</span>)<br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="5-text-参数"><a href="#5-text-参数" class="headerlink" title="5. text 参数"></a>5. text 参数</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter hljs"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs python">t_list = bs.find_all(text=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;hao123&quot;</span>)<span class="hljs-comment">#输入需要查找的文本关键字</span><br>t_list = bs.find_all(text=[<span class="hljs-string">&quot;hao123&quot;</span>,<span class="hljs-string">&quot;地图&quot;</span>,<span class="hljs-string">&quot;视频&quot;</span>])<span class="hljs-comment">#列表</span><br>t_list = bs.find_all(text = re.<span class="hljs-built_in">compile</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;\d&quot;</span>))<span class="hljs-comment">#正则查找标签里的字符串</span><br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>也可以应用正则表达式来查找包含特定文本的内容</li></ul><h3 id="6-limit-参数"><a href="#6-limit-参数" class="headerlink" title="6.limit 参数"></a>6.limit 参数</h3><table><thead><tr><th align="center">方法</th><th align="center">效果</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="center">limit</td><td align="center">获取到信息时选择获取几个信息</td></tr></tbody></table><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter hljs"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs python">t_list = bs.find_all(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;a&#x27;</span>,limit=<span class="hljs-number">3</span>)<span class="hljs-comment">#只获取3条数据</span><br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="7-CSS选择器"><a href="#7-CSS选择器" class="headerlink" title="7.CSS选择器"></a>7.CSS选择器</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter hljs"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs python">t_list = bs.select(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;title&#x27;</span>)<span class="hljs-comment">#通过标签来查找</span><br>t_list = bs.select(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;.mnav&#x27;</span>)<span class="hljs-comment">#通过类名来查找</span><br>t_list = bs.select(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;#u1&#x27;</span>)<span class="hljs-comment">#通过ID来查找</span><br>t_list = bs.select(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;a[class=&quot;bri&quot;]&#x27;</span>)<span class="hljs-comment">#通过属性来查找</span><br>t_list = bs.select(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;head &gt; title&#x27;</span>)<span class="hljs-comment">#通过子标签来查找</span><br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h2 id="文档的遍历-遍历文件树"><a href="#文档的遍历-遍历文件树" class="headerlink" title="文档的遍历/遍历文件树"></a>文档的遍历/遍历文件树</h2><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter hljs"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> bs4 <span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> BeautifulSoup<br>file = <span class="hljs-built_in">open</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;目标文件&quot;</span>,<span class="hljs-string">&quot;rb&quot;</span>)<br>html = file.read()<br>bs = BeautifulSoup(html,<span class="hljs-string">&quot;html.parser&quot;</span>)<br><br>print(bs.head.contents)<br>print(bs.head.contents[<span class="hljs-number">1</span>])<br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure><table><thead><tr><th align="center">方法</th><th align="center">效果</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="center">.contents</td><td align="center">获取Tag所有子节点，返回一个list</td></tr></tbody></table><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter hljs"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs python">print(bs.head.contents[<span class="hljs-number">1</span>])<br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>以列表索引来获取它的某一个元素</li></ul><blockquote><p>只展示一种方法其他的网上找</p><p>查找的进准度不如搜索来得实在</p></blockquote><hr><h2 id="过程备份："><a href="#过程备份：" class="headerlink" title="过程备份："></a>过程备份：</h2><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter hljs"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br><span class="line">55</span><br><span class="line">56</span><br><span class="line">57</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs python"><br><span class="hljs-comment"># BeautifulSoup将复杂的HTML文档转换成一个复杂的树形结构，</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 每个节点都是python对象，对所有对象可以归纳为4种：</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># - Tag</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># - NavigableString</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># - BeautifulSoup</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># - Comment</span><br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> bs4 <span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> BeautifulSoup<br><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> re<br><br><br>file = <span class="hljs-built_in">open</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;F:/编辑区/douban/test/baidu.html&quot;</span>,<span class="hljs-string">&quot;rb&quot;</span>)  <span class="hljs-comment">#模拟爬取到的文件读取并打开</span><br>html = file.read()  <span class="hljs-comment">#读取到一个对象中</span><br>bs = BeautifulSoup(html,<span class="hljs-string">&quot;html.parser&quot;</span>)  <span class="hljs-comment">#使用“html.parser”解析器解析一个之前定义的html对象</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment">#编译一个正则表达式对象，通过find_all()方法查找符合的对象</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># t_list = bs.find_all(re.compile(&quot;a&quot;))</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># print(t_list)</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment">#方法(函数)方式搜索</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># def name_is_exists(tag):</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">#     return tag.has_attr(&quot;name&quot;)</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># t_list = bs.find_all(name_is_exists)</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># # print(t_list)</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># for item in t_list:</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">#     print(item)</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment">#传参查找</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># t_list = bs.find_all(id=&quot;head&quot;)</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># print(t_list)</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># t_list = bs.find_all(class_=True)</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># for i in t_list:</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">#     print(i)</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># t_list = bs.find_all(href=&quot;http://tieba.baidu.com&quot;)</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># for i in t_list:</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">#     print(i)</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment">#text参数</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># t_list = bs.find_all(text=&quot;hao123&quot;)</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># t_list = bs.find_all(text=[&quot;hao123&quot;,&quot;地图&quot;,&quot;贴吧&quot;,&quot;视频&quot;])</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># t_list = bs.find_all(text = re.compile(&quot;\d&quot;))</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># t_list = bs.find_all(&#x27;a&#x27;,limit=3)</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># for i in t_list:</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">#     print(i)</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment">#CSS选择器</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># t_list = bs.select(&#x27;title&#x27;)#通过标签来查找</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># t_list = bs.select(&#x27;.mnav&#x27;)#通过类名来查找</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># t_list = bs.select(&#x27;#u1&#x27;)    #通过ID来查找</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># t_list = bs.select(&#x27;a[class=&quot;bri&quot;]&#x27;)#通过属性来查找</span><br>t_list = bs.select(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;head &gt; title&#x27;</span>)<br><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> i <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> t_list:<br>    print(i)<br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
